reviewText: Love this! Got it for my mom for Christmas. Came in perfect condition and worth every penny!

I watched this movie when it first came out in the 80's, and have wanted to see it again.  Its a very hard movie to find, and its kind of spendy, but well worth my money.  Rikki Lake, I don't really like her, but this was the best movie she ever made.  It deals with out of the ordinary people, and I can relate.

This movie is a gem. Finally what true love is all about. You can be heavy and get the guy. I love it. Ricki and Craig did a fanastic job in this film. I love when Ricki character says "silk pajamas sugar baby.' amoure. You'll love it. Buy it today or rent it.
